OL,3,CBeaulieu School to reopen after water
OL,4,Csupply turned back on
OL,6,FBeaulieu School in will reopen on
OL,7,FWednesday 22 May after it had to
OL,8,Ftemporarily close its doors due to
OL,9,Fleaking pipes.
OL,11,FAll students, except for those sitting
OL,12,Fexams, were asked to stay at home
OL,13,Fwhilst repair works were carried out.
OL,15,Fwas called out after water was
OL,16,Fdiscovered pooling on the playground
OL,17,Fon Monday 20 May.
