OL,3,CBeaulieu School to reopen after water
OL,4,Csupply turned back on
OL,6,FThe utilities company originally
OL,7,Fthought repairs could be made
OL,8,Fovernight, however, this was not
OL,9,Fpossible and the school had to close
OL,10,Ffor the day.
OL,12,FStudents with exams were asked to
OL,13,Fbring in their own water bottles, as
OL,14,Fthe school's water supply had to be
OL,15,Fcut off whilst repairs were carried
OL,16,Fout.
