OL,3,CBeaulieu School to reopen after water
OL,4,Csupply turned back on
OL,6,FDeputy Head Paul Curran said: "It took
OL,7,Fsome time to find the source of the
OL,8,Fleak but, once we had, it became clear
OL,9,Fthat it wasn't going to be possible to
OL,10,Fget the fix done ahead of school
OL,11,Fopening."
OL,13,FThe school said they prioritized their
OL,14,Fresources to ensure that the Year 6
OL,15,FSATS examinations, and the various
OL,16,FGCSE and A-Level exams could go ahead
OL,17,Fas planned.
