OL,3,CBeaulieu School to reopen after water
OL,4,Csupply turned back on
OL,6,FDeputy Head Paul Curran added: "Our
OL,7,Fteaching staff have been hard at work
OL,8,Ffrom home organising online tasks for
OL,9,Four students to complete.
OL,11,F"The leak has now been stopped and we
OL,12,Fare able to open again tomorrow at
OL,13,Ffull capacity."
OL,15,FHe added that Jersey Water were
OL,16,F"amazing", as they supported Beaulieu
OL,17,Fto resolve the leak, after they failed
OL,18,Fto find a plumber at short notice out
OL,19,Fof hours.
