OL,3,CBeaulieu School to reopen after water
OL,4,Csupply turned back on
OL,6,FThe leaking pipework was in the
OL,7,Fschool's private water supply, rather
OL,8,Fthan in Jersey Water's mains
OL,9,Fconnection.
OL,11,FFurther works have been scheduled to
OL,12,Ffully repair the leak however, these
OL,13,Fwill be carried out over the half term
OL,14,Fto avoid disruption.
